com.interpss.dstab

Interface BaseDStabBus<TGen extends DStabGen,TLoad extends DStabLoad>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseAclfBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAcscBus, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DStabBus, Dynamic3PBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseDStabBusImpl, DStabBusImpl, Dynamic3PBusImpl

    public interface BaseDStabBus<TGen extends DStabGen,TLoad extends DStabLoad>
extends BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, IDynamicSimulation
    A representation of the model object 'DStab Bus'. Bus class for hosting bus stability study information.

    The following features are supported:

    • Init Load
    • Init Volt Mag
    • Load Model Switched
    • Freq
    • Bus Freq Measure Block
    • Dynamic Event
    • Dynamic Bus Device List
    See Also:
    DstabPackage.getBaseDStabBus()
